amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetCount              amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetCount

   NAME
	AtpFeedGetCount -- Number of posts in a feed object.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	n = AtpFeedGetCount(feed);
	ULONG AtpFeedGetCount(struct AtpFeed *feed);

   FUNCTION
	Returns how many posts were parsed into the feed page.

   RESULTS
	Count, or 0 if feed is NULL/invalid.  Capped at 50 posts per page.

   SEE ALSO
	AtpFeedGetPost(), AtpGetTimeline()
amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetCursor             amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetCursor

   NAME
	AtpFeedGetCursor -- Opaque pagination cursor for the next page.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	cursor = AtpFeedGetCursor(feed);
	STRPTR AtpFeedGetCursor(struct AtpFeed *feed);

   FUNCTION
	Returns the "cursor" string from getTimeline / getAuthorFeed, or NULL
	if there is no further page.  Pass to the next AtpGetTimeline() /
	AtpGetAuthorFeed() call.

   RESULTS
	Library-owned STRPTR until DisposeAtpFeed().

   SEE ALSO
	AtpGetTimeline(), AtpGetAuthorFeed()
amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetPost               amiatp.library/AtpFeedGetPost

   NAME
	AtpFeedGetPost -- Pointer to the Nth post in a feed.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	post = AtpFeedGetPost(feed, index);
	struct AtpFeedPost *AtpFeedGetPost(struct AtpFeed *feed, ULONG index);

   FUNCTION
	Returns an opaque post pointer for use with AtpFeedPostGet*().
	index is 0-based.  The pointer is owned by the feed.

   RESULTS
	Post pointer, or NULL if out of range / invalid feed.

   SEE ALSO
	AtpFeedGetCount(), AtpFeedPostGetText()
amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetAuthorHandle   amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetAuthorHandle

   NAME
	AtpFeedPostGetAuthorHandle -- Author handle of a feed post.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
