	Library-owned STRPTR until DisposeAtpFeed(), or NULL.
amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetAvatarUrl      amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetAvatarUrl

   NAME
	AtpFeedPostGetAvatarUrl -- Author avatar CDN URL.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	url = AtpFeedPostGetAvatarUrl(post);
	STRPTR AtpFeedPostGetAvatarUrl(struct AtpFeedPost *post);

   FUNCTION
