amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetImageCount     amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetImageCount

   NAME
	AtpFeedPostGetImageCount -- Number of embed image thumbs (0..4).  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	n = AtpFeedPostGetImageCount(post);
	ULONG AtpFeedPostGetImageCount(struct AtpFeedPost *post);

   FUNCTION
	Counts thumb (or fullsize) URLs collected from embed views:
	app.bsky.embed.images#view, recordWithMedia media.images, and
	external.thumb.  At most 4 URLs are stored per post.

   RESULTS
	0..4.

   SEE ALSO
	AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl()
amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl       amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl

   NAME
	AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl -- Embed image thumb/fullsize URL by index.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	url = AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl(post, index);
	STRPTR AtpFeedPostGetImageUrl(struct AtpFeedPost *post, ULONG index);

   FUNCTION
	Returns one stored embed image URL.

   INPUTS
	post  - Feed post.
	index - 0-based; must be < AtpFeedPostGetImageCount(post).

   RESULTS
	Library-owned URL, or NULL if out of range.

   SEE ALSO
	AtpFeedPostGetImageCount(), AtpDownloadUrl()
amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetText           amiatp.library/AtpFeedPostGetText

   NAME
	AtpFeedPostGetText -- Post body text from the Lexicon record.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
	text = AtpFeedPostGetText(post);
	STRPTR AtpFeedPostGetText(struct AtpFeedPost *post);

   FUNCTION
	Returns record.text from the feed view.  May be UTF-8; the app is
	responsible for display folding (e.g. Seiten utf8fold).

